      <Item ItemId=";teamstoolkit.viewsWelcome.teamsfx-empty-project-with-chat-preview-tag.content" ItemType="0" PsrId="306" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[Welcome to Microsoft 365 Agents Toolkit!]A;Get started with a guided tutorial]A;[Build a Declarative Agent]5D;(command:fx-extension.buildIntelligentAppsWalkthrough?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A; Or jump right into the app development with app templates or samples]A;[Create a New Agent/App]5D;(command:fx-extension.create?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;[View Samples]5D;(command:fx-extension.openSamples?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;Visit our documentation to build apps for [Microsoft Teams]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-apps%22%5D) or extend [Microsoft 365 Copilot]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-agents%22%5D).]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[Ti diamo il benvenuto nel toolkit per gli agenti Microsoft 365.]A;Inizia con un'esercitazione guidata]A;[Crea un agente dichiarativo]5D;(command:fx-extension.buildIntelligentAppsWalkthrough?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A; In alternativa, passa direttamente allo sviluppo di app con modelli o esempi]A;[Crea un nuovo agente/app]5D;(command:fx-extension.create?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;[Visualizza esempi]5D;(command:fx-extension.openSamples?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;Vedere la documentazione per creare app per [Microsoft Teams]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-apps%22%5D) o estendere [Microsoft 365 Copilot]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-agents%22%5D).]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
          <Prev Cat="Text">
            <Val><![CDATA[Welcome to Microsoft 365 Agents Toolkit!]A;Get started with a guided tutorial]A;[Build a Declarative Agent]5D;(command:fx-extension.buildIntelligentAppsWalkthrough?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A; Or jump right into the app development with app templates or samples]A;[Create a New Agent/App]5D;(command:fx-extension.create?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;[View Samples]5D;(command:fx-extension.openSamples?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;Create your new app effortlessly with GitHub Copilot. ]A;[Create App with GitHub Copilot (Preview)]5D;(command:fx-extension.invokeChatWithPreviewTag?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;Visit our documentation to build apps for [Microsoft Teams]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-apps%22%5D) or extend [Microsoft 365 Copilot]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-agents%22%5D).]]></Val>
          </Prev>
        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
      <Item ItemId=";teamstoolkit.viewsWelcome.teamsfx-empty-project-with-chat.content" ItemType="0" PsrId="306" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[Welcome to Microsoft 365 Agents Toolkit!]A;Get started with a guided tutorial]A;[Build a Declarative Agent]5D;(command:fx-extension.buildIntelligentAppsWalkthrough?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A; Or jump right into the app development with app templates or samples]A;[Create a New Agent/App]5D;(command:fx-extension.create?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;[View Samples]5D;(command:fx-extension.openSamples?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;Create your new app effortlessly with GitHub Copilot.]A;[Create App with GitHub Copilot]5D;(command:fx-extension.invokeChat?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;Visit our documentation to build apps for [Microsoft Teams]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-apps%22%5D) or extend [Microsoft 365 Copilot]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-agents%22%5D).]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[Benvenuto nel toolkit per gli agenti Microsoft 365.]A;Inizia con un'esercitazione guidata]A;[Crea un agente dichiarativo]5D;(command:fx-extension.buildIntelligentAppsWalkthrough?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A; In alternativa, passa direttamente allo sviluppo di app con modelli o esempi]A;[Crea un nuovo agente/app]5D;(command:fx-extension.create?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;[Visualizza esempi]5D;(command:fx-extension.openSamples?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;È possibile creare con facilità una nuova app con GitHub Copilot.]A;[Crea l'app con GitHub Copilot]5D;(command:fx-extension.invokeChat?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;Vedere la documentazione per creare app per [Microsoft Teams]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-apps%22%5D) o estendere [Microsoft 365 Copilot]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-agents%22%5D).]]></Val>
