            <Val><![CDATA[Welcome to Microsoft 365 Agents Toolkit!]A;Get started with a guided tutorial]A;[Build a Declarative Agent]5D;(command:fx-extension.buildIntelligentAppsWalkthrough?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A; Or jump right into the app development with app templates or samples]A;[Create a New Agent/App]5D;(command:fx-extension.create?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;[View Samples]5D;(command:fx-extension.openSamples?%5B%22SideBar%22%5D)]A;Visit our documentation to build apps for [Microsoft Teams]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-apps%22%5D) or extend [Microsoft 365 Copilot]5D;(command:fx-extension.openDocument?%5B%22documentName%22%2C%22build-agents%22%5D).]]></Val>
