          <Val><![CDATA[Explore these resources to build intelligent apps and enhance your development projects]A;🗒️ [Generative AI for Beginners]5D;(https://github.com/microsoft/generative-ai-for-beginners/tree/main)]A;✨ [Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG)]5D;(https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/search/retrieval-augmented-generation-overview)]A;📚 [AI Learning and Community Hub]5D;(https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/ai/)]]></Val>
